PrecisOrder, under subsection 27(1.1) of the SPECIES AT RISK ACT, deciding not to add the Bering Cisco and the Black Redhorse to Schedule 1 and to refer the assessment of the ghost antler back to the Committee on the Status of Endangered Wildlife in Canada for further information or consideration.
